<emphasis bold="true" box="[174,308,3054,3087]" pageId="208" pageNumber="486">Breeding.</emphasis>
Two female Turimiquire Climbing Rats captured by the Smithsonian Venezuelan Project in June-July had four embryos and one had five embryos.
</paragraph>
